<td><p>pick_mode :</p></td>
<td><p>how the scene graph should be painted</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>x :</p></td>
<td><p>X coordinate to check</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>y :</p></td>
<td><p>Y coordinate to check</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>Returns :</p></td>
